CHANGES IN VERSION 1.8.0
------------------------

    o Bringing in Josh Zitovsky's work on fast beta binomial
      GLM fitting in C++.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.5.4
------------------------

    o Added possibility for weights and standard errors to bbEstDisp().
      The standard errors are for the log of dispersion (theta).

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.3.2
------------------------

    o Fix simple bug when no sample has only intercept coefficient.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.2.0
------------------------

    o Faster fitting of Negative Binomial using RcppNumerical.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.0
------------------------

    o apeglm is released on Bioconductor! Methods can be accessed
      from within DESeq2 by calling 'lfcShrink' with type="apeglm".
